sequenceDiagram
    participant Cam as ESP32-CAM
    participant Vision as VisionService
    participant Face as FaceService
    participant Ctrl as Controller
    participant Mqtt as MQTT Broker
    participant IO as ESP32-C3
    participant UI as Web/Mobile

    Vision->>Cam: GET /capture
    Cam-->>Vision: JPEG frame
    Vision->>Face: classify(frame)
    Face-->>Vision: label, confidence, distance
    Vision->>Ctrl: handle_vision_result(...)

    alt owner
        Ctrl->>Mqtt: publish home/io/cmd/door OPEN
    else stranger
        Ctrl->>Mqtt: publish home/io/cmd/door CLOSE
    else no_face
        Ctrl-->>Ctrl: keep safe state
    end

    IO->>Mqtt: publish home/io/telemetry
    Ctrl->>UI: update status/events
